  <description><![CDATA[<p>A pioneering hotel in terms of architecture and sustainability, The Design Hotel Eden is the first hotel in Selva to have specialised in environmentally-friendly construction. The Eden is built in smart Alpine style using an abundance of wood and light to make the most of the mountain views. Warm and attentive service is assured from your hosts Roland and Raffaella as is a comfortable, intimate atmosphere. Ski back to this hotel, only 100m from the Ciampinoi chairlift and 5 minutes’ walk (450m) to the centre of resort. The Eden also boasts a wellness centre with sauna and steam room as well as an outdoor whirlpool.</p>]]></description>
